MatConnect — Actual Feature List

Check-in & Front Desk

- Self-service kiosk — tablet check-in, no staff needed
- QR / token check-in — members check in via a personal QR code
- Walk-in support — sell to or check in non-members
- Check-in sources tracked: kiosk, staff, app

Member Management

- Full profiles — photo, contact, address, date of birth, age group (kids/adult)
- Family accounts — parent/child linking with automatic family discounts
- Belt rank + belt stripes tracking
- Training type (Gi / No-Gi / Both)
- Status lifecycle: lead → trial → active → past due → canceled → inactive
- Staff notes, attendance history, waiver history per member
- At-risk member view — flags members likely to churn

Belt Progression & Curriculum

- Per-rank requirements — minimum classes, months, and techniques to promote
- Technique progress tracking per member
- Curriculum builder — multi-week lesson plans with warmups, techniques, video links, day-of-week scheduling
- Members track their own progress toward the next belt

Class Scheduling

- Recurring + one-off classes
- Programs/class types (Gi, No-Gi, Youth, Seminar, Intro, Private)
- Instructor assignment, capacity limits
- Live rosters, booking + waitlist support, no-show tracking

Billing & Payments

- Stripe and Square supported (switchable payment provider)
- Recurring membership subscriptions
- Card on file, new card, cash, and Square Terminal (in-person card reader)
- Failed-payment retries / dunning
- Trials with configurable trial length
- Point of Sale — retail/gear/day passes, barcode scanning, inventory/stock, tax rates, cash drawer

Marketing & Automation

- Automation workflows triggered by: trial attendance, inactivity, birthday, failed payment, belt promotion
- Multi-channel messaging — email, SMS, web push, in-app
- Lead capture widget (embeddable) + leads pipeline
- Self-serve enrollment flow
- Automated class reminders & waiver reminders (cron-driven)
- Email/SMS powered by Brevo

Member Portal (this exists — earlier doc was wrong)

- Profile, schedule, attendance history, curriculum, and progress views
- Payment method management
- Web push notifications

Admin & Operations

- Reports/analytics
- Staff user accounts & roles
- Feature visibility toggles (hide modules you don't use)
- Square data import (migrate customers/subscriptions/payments)
- Multi-currency, locale, and timezone settings
- Guided setup wizard

The real gaps are predictive churn scoring, multi-location, 

native mobile, and website builder.


